<h2>September 2024 Events in Europe</h2>
<p>September is full of excitement and energy in Europe. From sailing regattas to alpine rallies and book festivals, here are a few of our <span style="font-size: 14px;">favourite</span> events over the coming weeks.</p>
<p><img style="width: 100%; height: auto;" src="/media/2159/venice_big.jpg?width=500&amp;height=238.69047619047618" alt="september events europe" data-udi="umb://media/3c68cbbf442d4f65a377c6d6d7d7ff5b" /></p>
<p>Europe is teeming with cultural treats and outdoor adventures. Whether you want to explore the wonders of Venice, hike the Austrian Alps, September is a great month for visiting Europe's treasures.</p>
<p>We've selected our top picks to get you started. Grab your passport and start planning your itinerary.</p>
<h3>2024 September Events in Europe</h3>
<p><a href="#regatta" data-anchor="#regatta">Historical Venice Regatta</a> | <a href="#bardolino" data-anchor="#bardolino">Bardolino wine festival</a> | <a href="#red" data-anchor="#red">Red Bull 400 Planica</a> | <a href="#mile" data-anchor="#mile">Culinary Mile</a> |</p>
</div>
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h2 id="regatta" style="text-align: left;">Historical Venice Regatta</h2>
<br />
<h3>Where: <a data-udi="umb://document/201893063f65496384a9bd17846543a7" href="/{localLink:umb://document/201893063f65496384a9bd17846543a7}" title="Venice">Venice</a>, Italy</h3>
<h3>When: 1st September 2024</h3>
<p><img style="width: 100%; height: auto;" src="/media/13092032/adobestock_454185035.jpg?width=500&amp;height=281.25" alt="september events" data-udi="umb://media/dd8963eb7ab345588ba77ee0ece726ac" /></p>
<p>Italy's Venice Historical Regatta is a boat parade that allows you to experience the sights, sounds and excitement of Venice in a whole new way.</p>
<p>This highly anticipated annual event takes place on the first Sunday of September, and combines the spirit of this ancient city with one of its best known traditions - <a rel="noopener" href="https://veneziaautentica.com/venetian-rowing/#:~:text=The%20%E2%80%9CVoga%20Veneta%E2%80%9D%20or%20Venetian,because%20it%20is%20extremely%20efficient." target="_blank" data-anchor="#:~:text=The%20%E2%80%9CVoga%20Veneta%E2%80%9D%20or%20Venetian,because%20it%20is%20extremely%20efficient.">Venetian rowing</a>.</p>
<p>The event begins with a parade of dozens of brightly painted boats, each with its own gondolier in costume. The parade starts near Saint Mark’s Square and travels along the Grand Canal before returning to Ca' Foscari University, where people gather along the canal to cheer and watch the boats pass by.</p>
<p>If you are planning a trip to Venice in September, make sure you make note of this very special event.</p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;"><a rel="noopener" href="https://www.regatastoricavenezia.it/en/" target="_blank" title="Historial regatta" class="c-btn">Find Out More</a></span></p>
</div>
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<p> </p>
<h2 id="bardolino" style="text-align: left;">Bardolino Wine Festival</h2>
<p> </p>
<h3><strong>Where: <a data-udi="umb://document/ae52b40037474a3eadb1c0692c464473" href="/{localLink:umb://document/ae52b40037474a3eadb1c0692c464473}" title="Lake Garda">Lake Garda</a>, Italy</strong></h3>
<h3>When: 9th September-7th October 2024</h3>
<p><img style="width: 100%; height: auto;" src="/media/13098694/adobestock_231727725.jpg?width=500&amp;height=268.49642004773267" alt="Bardolino wine festival" data-udi="umb://media/188087af4da443f9ad79b6cacb92b262" /></p>
<p>Wine lovers, mark your calendars.</p>
<p>The Bardolino Wine Festival is an annual celebration, that marks the maturation and distribution of the Bardolino wine, turning the arrival of autumn into a grape affair.</p>
<p>Wine lovers from all over the region flock to Lake Garda to sip, swirl, and savour some of the finest wines.</p>
<p>With our holidays extending until the end of October, you'll have the opportunity to explore Italy's Lake Garda and take part in the exciting festivities.</p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;"><a rel="noopener" href="https://www.carnifest.com/bardolino-wine-festival-2023/" target="_blank" title="Bardolino Wine Festival" class="c-btn">Find Out More</a></span></p>
</div>
<div class="white_box_shadow"><span style="font-weight: 400;"><a rel="noopener" href="https://www.redbull.com/si-sl/events/400-planica" target="_blank" title="Red Bull 400" class="c-btn"></a></span></div>
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<p> </p>
<h2 id="mile" style="text-align: left;">Culinary Mile</h2>
<br />
<h3>Where: <a data-udi="umb://document/ae93f514436f422b8a051f43d7310e8e" href="/{localLink:umb://document/ae93f514436f422b8a051f43d7310e8e}" title="Saas Fee">Saas Fee</a>, Switzerland<span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></h3>
<h3>When: 8th September<strong> 2024</strong></h3>
<p><img style="width: 100%; height: auto;" src="/media/13092035/adobestock_219911560.jpg?width=500&amp;height=281.25" alt="europe events september" data-udi="umb://media/687cce2d7cb44a98bd51880a652e2806" /></p>
<p>In September, the much-loved Culinary Mile returns to Saas-Fee. Hoteliers and restaurateurs will gather along the main street to showcase food and beverages that have a nostalgic twist. It's an excellent opportunity to experience the unique culture and cuisine of the Valais, with many different menu selections and a variety of local wines to taste. Visitors are encouraged to come dressed up in old-fashioned costume, there is even a best dressed prize for both adults and children.</p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;"><a rel="noopener" href="https://www.saas-fee.ch/en/events/top-events-in-summer/nostalgic-culinary-mile" target="_blank" title="Culinary Mile Saas Fee" class="c-btn">Find Out More</a></span></p>
</div>
<p> </p>
